<div class="bio" data-idx="1" style="display: none;">
	<h2>Arié Botbol</h2>
	<p>Born in 1967 in Marocco, Arié BOTBOL has kept deeply within himself the tastes, lights and refinement of his oriental origins.
	His first great photographic emotions are naturally emerged under the lights of Mediterranean. But rapidly, his curious and traveler mind takes him shooting his camera toward other horizons and cultures. 
	<p>Combining his background as the founder of a communication agency in Paris, with his passion for photography, he tells simple stories and creates rigorous compositions with soft and living atmospheres.
	His images are often full and frontal. He likes to capture the natural geometry of our environment and spontaneously stage the human in his compositions.
	His first exhibition «Ailleurs, Exactement» took place in June 2014 in the Gallery of Laverie (Paris).
	</p>
</div>
