	<p>Evel Gonzalez was born in 1968 in La Havana. He studied graphic journalism and photography in La Havana University.
	He settled in Venezuela in 1993 where he worked as a press photographer, as well as in several south or central American countries : Colombia, Panama, Dominican Republic, Mexico, Haiti, Ecuador and Salvador. 
